<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Fotos de Leandro Fabian Jr.</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-sans">

  <section class="relative bg-cover bg-center h-screen" style="background-image: url('{{hero.url}}')">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 flex justify-center items-center h-full text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">Fotos</h1>
      <p class="text-xl ml-2">
        de Leandro Fabian Jr.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">
        Às vezes faço umas fotos em viagens e passeios.<br />Instagram dá trabalho e é muito limitado, então coloco as
        fotos
        aqui.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 mx-auto">
        {{#each colunas}}
        <div class="grid gap-4">
          {{#each this}}
          <div>
            <img class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" src="{{this.url}}" alt="{{this.url}}" />
          </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <a href="https://instagram.com/leandrofabianjr" target="_blank"
          class="mx-4 text-xl hover:text-yellow-500 transition duration-300">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://leandrofabianjr.com" target="_blank"
          class="mx-4 text-xl hover:text-yellow-500 transition duration-300">Website</a>
      </div>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Leandro Fabian Jr. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>